  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/9a6c7ff6efcbb93daf9ee3a8c4dd1f20.avif?t=1773917939\" width=2048 height=1269 /></span></p></p><br><h1>BUG REPORT</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/14e361116969a15a531c297a69bba8b3.avif?t=1773917939\" width=800 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can join 'Discord' via the link on the Steam store page.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Inspiration from...</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The gory thrills of giallo, the suspense of slashers, and the otherworldly charm of 70s and 80s sci-fi.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>We're thrilled to bring you a chilling adventure that blends cinematic horror with the nostalgic vibes of '90s 16-bit games.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to Save the Game?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After waking from the nightmare and answering the mysterious phone call, Sarah can unlock manual saving by interacting with the cigarette pack in the kitchen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How to use it:</strong> In your inventory, drag the cigarette onto the lighter to bring up the save menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/9ed56c160322e3b3035f033f6b411867.poster.avif?t=1773917939\" width=490 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/9ed56c160322e3b3035f033f6b411867.webm?t=1773917939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/9ed56c160322e3b3035f033f6b411867.mp4?t=1773917939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/0fda0b5015bb82a5e586602cbcb4ecf5.avif?t=1773917939\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras_big/0fda0b5015bb82a5e586602cbcb4ecf5.avif?t=1773917939 width=800 height=231 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/00e0e0d3f39045a00f8547a57da09fba.avif?t=1773917939\" width=616 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Midnight Special</i></strong> is a point-and-click survival horror experience that echoes the spirit of '90s classics like Clock Tower and Resident Evil. Set in the late '80s at Boyd Manor, you step into the shoes of Sarah, a babysitter tasked with watching over Jon and Ellie Boyd for the night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What begins as an ordinary evening takes a sinister turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The power goes out, plunging the house into pitch-black darkness. With each step, reality twists into something far more disturbing.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bizarre phone calls, a deranged stalker perhaps?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unpleasant odors seeping up from the floorboards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Objects moving on their own as if possessed.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A life-sized plastic dinosaur that seems... alive.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Has Sarah lost her mind? Or has something far more sinister taken root?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/21aaedda2c7e17536162c58a5d24dee7.poster.avif?t=1773917939\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/21aaedda2c7e17536162c58a5d24dee7.webm?t=1773917939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/21aaedda2c7e17536162c58a5d24dee7.mp4?t=1773917939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/00e0e0d3f39045a00f8547a57da09fba.avif?t=1773917939\" width=616 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/3813e48e5f44eb311ad4f0d42011a253.avif?t=1773917939\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic Point-and-Click Survival Horror</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a foreboding environment filled with chilling surprises, puzzles to solve, and secrets to uncover.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Tribute to Retro Horror</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Influenced by '70s and '80s horror cinema and '90s gaming, <i><strong>Midnight Special</strong></i> blends nostalgia with heart-pounding suspense.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric 16-Bit Graphics</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gorgeous handcrafted visuals capture the eerie, cinematic tone in stunning pixel art.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Psychological Thrills</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Question everything as reality twists and warps around you. Can you trust what you see?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Audio Design</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An immersive, spine-tingling soundtrack and unnerving audio cues heighten the tension with every step you take.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/647e56785c433a6780a551bfa79aabbf.poster.avif?t=1773917939\" width=800 height=592 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/647e56785c433a6780a551bfa79aabbf.webm?t=1773917939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/647e56785c433a6780a551bfa79aabbf.mp4?t=1773917939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/00e0e0d3f39045a00f8547a57da09fba.avif?t=1773917939\" width=616 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/869fc26c121ac9549eb45c4746347068.avif?t=1773917939\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With its carefully woven narrative, <i><strong>Midnight Special</strong></i> invites players to step into a story of <strong>psychological terror and mystery</strong>. Every corner holds a secret, and every clue leads you deeper into a horrifying truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you're a fan of:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic survival horror</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Point-and-click adventures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric mysteries that keep you guessing</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...then <i><strong>Midnight Special</strong></i> is ready to pull you into the darkness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you dare enter the manor?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/d60002d9d0c21483a5d2af92d1851180.poster.avif?t=1773917939\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/d60002d9d0c21483a5d2af92d1851180.webm?t=1773917939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/d60002d9d0c21483a5d2af92d1851180.mp4?t=1773917939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/00e0e0d3f39045a00f8547a57da09fba.avif?t=1773917939\" width=616 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560100/extras/4660f0612be186e35c4f1c52eaf94cd2.avif?t=1773917939\" width=616 height=349 /></span></p>",
